hope for the future said ruben z vartanyan who sought asylum 
at the us embassy in bolivia last week while visiting that nation 
i am an outspoken person vartanyan told a washington news 
conference i could not disguise my feelings vartanyan said 
and he believes that informers reported back to the authorities 
vartanyan said he first experienced trouble on his return to 
moscow in 1976 after a stay of nearly six years in bolivia where 
