disaster and now the fires there are always hurdles in the road 
this is just another one i try to be philosophical 
wanna buy a tshirt cheap 
povahs quip is typical of the kind of humor he says has helped 
his family cope with mother nature and washington bureaucrats 
during the nearly three quarters of a century hamilton stores has 
been in yellowstone 
we basically fly with one eye open anyway said povah 
whos to say in august of 88 that we wont have a gas shortage 
