work in the cinema for 15 years 
two other soviet films are being shown as retrospective pieces 
the onset of an unknown age made two decades ago to 
commemorate the october revolution and asyas happiness 
directed by andrei konchalovsky a film soviet leader mikhail 
gorbachev has called one of the best movies hes seen in years 
