president daniel ortega cancelled on 
thursday his scheduled visit to the united nations because the us 
government delayed visas for about two dozen members of his 
delegation a government official announced 
this arbitrary and illegal attitude constitutes a denial of 
nicaraguan rights deputy foreign minister victor hugo tinoco 
