financerelated issue facing it whether the owners are 
financially qualified to operate the plant 
seabrook officials expressed confidence the decommissioning 
question would be resolved in their favor 
were in the process of answering those questions right now 
and were confident this wont be an issue barring us from 
lowpower testing said ronald a sher spokesman for the 
reactors owner 
